      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine starts up reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a consistent and comfortable driving experience. While there may be minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. This is a dependable car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
